WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.790
Hey, good morning everybody. I'm Brandon

00:00:02.790 --> 00:00:02.800
Biggs

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:05.309
and this is Diana Biggs, and we're so

00:00:05.319 --> 00:00:07.990
blessed you joined us today. You know, I

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.709
was praying on the couch last night and

00:00:09.719 --> 00:00:11.509
I said, "Lord, what do you have for

00:00:11.519 --> 00:00:14.990
your people today? I

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.230
need something

00:00:17.230 --> 00:00:17.240
fresh."He

00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:19.029
said, "I want you to go back to the

00:00:19.039 --> 00:00:21.230
authority of the believer. I want you to

00:00:21.240 --> 00:00:23.269
talk about the authority of the

00:00:23.269 --> 00:00:23.279
believer."I

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:25.390
said, "Well, I can do that, Lord,"and it's

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:28.029
one of my favorite topics.

00:00:28.039 --> 00:00:30.630
My son, Diana, and

00:00:30.630 --> 00:00:30.640
I

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:34.270
all love it; we've listened to it for

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:36.430
the last ten years, really

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:39.190
heavy, all the time. Even my son,

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:40.910
when he was a little boy,

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.670
could quote some sermons

00:00:42.680 --> 00:00:45.590
better than the preacher

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:48.310
could because he would

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.910
memorize what the preacher was

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:54.069
going to say. He would be like a

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:55.790
parrot as a little boy and

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.470
start quoting what he was fixing to say

00:00:57.480 --> 00:00:59.509
before he would say it. Even afterwards,

00:00:59.519 --> 00:01:02.069
when the sermon was over and

00:01:02.069 --> 00:01:02.079
we were

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:04.109
driving in the car,

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:08.910
he would always quote all of the

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:10.950
sermons we would listen to.

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:13.310
I'd play them on my MP3 player,

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:15.830
playing

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:18.390
one sermon continually on

00:01:18.390 --> 00:01:18.400
the radio because

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.429
I wanted to get it down inside of

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:22.310
me. Faith cometh by

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.510
hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:26.350
I know that the more you listen to

00:01:26.360 --> 00:01:28.950
it, the more it becomes real to you.

00:01:30.479 --> 00:01:32.389
I heard Brother Hagin say that he

00:01:32.399 --> 00:01:34.350
would listen to things and

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:36.270
meditate on the Word and get it down

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.389
inside him. I thought, "Well, if it

00:01:37.399 --> 00:01:39.830
worked for Brother Hagin and his

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:42.109
life was so fruitful,

00:01:44.600 --> 00:01:47.709
why not do it too?"So I

00:01:47.719 --> 00:01:49.230
started finding sermons that stood out

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:51.270
to me—Brother Hagin's sermons and

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:51.280
others—and

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.149
I just listened

00:01:53.149 --> 00:01:53.159
to them

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:55.270
over and over to the point where,

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:57.109
like I said, my son would

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:59.230
start quoting them. I'd go, "Well, I guess

00:01:59.240 --> 00:02:00.950
I've listened to that one long enough;

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:03.550
I need to move on to another

00:02:03.550 --> 00:02:03.560
one."Kenneth

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.830
E.

00:02:04.830 --> 00:02:04.840
Hagin—to

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:07.190
the point where, like I said, my

00:02:07.190 --> 00:02:07.200
son

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.949
knows his stories better

00:02:08.959 --> 00:02:11.630
than he

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:14.869
did. I say, "Wow, praise

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:17.589
the Lord!"I was

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:18.910
thinking about the sermon whenever he

00:02:18.920 --> 00:02:20.589
was talking about

00:02:20.589 --> 00:02:20.599
how

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:25.070
the power company provides the

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:27.790
power to the

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:30.949
house, just like the Father provides the

00:02:30.959 --> 00:02:33.790
authority and the power of His presence.

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:36.070
The anointing on

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.910
you provides the power, but it's our

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:42.190
job to flip the switch. He's not going to

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:45.869
flip the switch in your house. The Oklahoma

00:02:45.879 --> 00:02:48.869
Tulsa power company is not going to come

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:51.830
and turn the switch on in your house;

00:02:55.239 --> 00:02:57.830
they

00:02:57.840 --> 00:03:00.229
provided the power to the pole, but it's

00:03:00.239 --> 00:03:01.910
my job to flip the

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:05.750
switch. As believers, it's our job

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:08.710
to flip the

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:10.990
switch of the power like we do in

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:11.000
a

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:14.190
house. He's not going to flip it for

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:17.270
you. We are praying for the sick

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:19.670
and saying, "God,

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:22.030
why haven't you done

00:03:22.030 --> 00:03:22.040
this?"He's

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:23.390
already done it, ladies and gentlemen!

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:26.309
He's already said, "It is finished."Those

00:03:26.309 --> 00:03:26.319
were

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:28.670
His last words on the cross. What

00:03:28.670 --> 00:03:28.680
was

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:31.990
finished?

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:36.110
Everything He set out to do to

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:39.710
redeem us from the curse of the law was

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:42.949
finished. He redeemed us; He took our

00:03:42.959 --> 00:03:46.229
infirmities, our poverty,

00:03:46.239 --> 00:03:49.190
our grief, and our sorrows. He took

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:53.390
everything on Himself that was on

00:03:53.390 --> 00:03:53.400
us—everything

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:56.470
that the curse of the law of

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:59.309
Deuteronomy 28

00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:01.360
stated.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:05.710
According to Galatians,

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:08.550
Christ has redeemed us from the

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:09.589
curse of the

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:15.270
law by becoming those curses for us. So,

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:18.310
it's done. When He said it's

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:21.270
finished, it's finished. There's nothing

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:24.469
more He can do for you. He already

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:27.430
told you, "You are healed by the stripes

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:29.150
of

00:04:29.150 --> 00:04:29.160
Jesus."Isaiah

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:31.990
53:5 and 1

00:04:31.990 --> 00:04:32.000
Peter—those

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.029
scriptures are

00:04:35.039 --> 00:04:36.510
real, alive, and

00:04:36.520 --> 00:04:38.830
powerful today. They're

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:40.629
for every single one of

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:43.390
us if you just believe it. He has

00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:45.870
already provided healing,

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:48.189
health, wealth, wisdom,

00:04:48.199 --> 00:04:49.830
and all the things He said He would

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:51.830
do for us. It's our job to flip the

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:55.110
switch

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:58.749
in our spiritual house and say, "I

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:01.790
yield to what He already

00:05:01.790 --> 00:05:01.800
did."We

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:04.629
stand confidently in the finished

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:07.749
works of Jesus Christ,

00:05:09.590 --> 00:05:09.600
which

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:14.710
guarantees you victory. He's given us

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:17.350
dominion.

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:20.070
He also says to

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:23.670
heal the sick. He didn't say

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:26.749
pray for the sick; He said heal the sick.

00:05:28.280 --> 00:05:30.029
Matthew

00:05:30.039 --> 00:05:32.830
10:8 says, "Heal the sick, cleanse the lepers,

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:35.309
raise the dead, cast out devils; freely

00:05:35.319 --> 00:05:38.189
you have received, freely

00:05:38.189 --> 00:05:38.199
give."We're

00:05:38.199 --> 00:05:40.830
using our

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.909
authority right there.

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:49.430
James 4:7 says, "Submit yourself unto

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:53.309
God, resist the devil, and he will

00:05:53.309 --> 00:05:53.319
flee."He

00:05:53.319 --> 00:05:55.710
didn't say for you to pray and ask the

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:58.790
Lord to take care of the devil for you;

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:01.309
He said for you to

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:04.110
submit yourself unto God and resist him.

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:08.029
If you don't resist him, he isn't going

00:06:08.039 --> 00:06:09.350
to

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:11.589
flee.

00:06:11.589 --> 00:06:11.599
If

00:06:11.599 --> 00:06:13.550
you

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:16.830
resist him

00:06:16.830 --> 00:06:16.840
and

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:19.309
keep on keeping on, when he realizes that

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:20.950
you're not going to give up

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:24.230
and you are not going to cower down to

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:26.150
him, he's going to

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:29.110
flee. But it's not until you

00:06:29.110 --> 00:06:29.120
have

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:32.110
that

00:06:32.110 --> 00:06:32.120
bulldog

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:36.430
on a bone mentality—"I'm not letting go of

00:06:36.430 --> 00:06:36.440
my

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:39.950
God-given

00:06:39.960 --> 00:06:42.629
rights to walk in health,

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:45.309
healing,

00:06:45.319 --> 00:06:47.990
and

00:06:50.510 --> 00:06:50.520
deliverance"—that

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:55.469
he will

00:06:55.479 --> 00:06:58.749
flee in terror, like

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:01.309
Brother Hagin used to say.

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:02.790
He's going to run in terror,

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.830
freaking out to get out

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:07.550
of here, because

00:07:07.550 --> 00:07:07.560
he

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:10.350
knows when

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:16.510
you have that

00:07:16.520 --> 00:07:21.189
revelation of authority to tread

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:23.670
on serpents and scorpions and nothing

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:26.510
shall by any means hurt you. That's what

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:27.749
Jesus

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:30.270
said: "A thousand shall fall at my

00:07:30.280 --> 00:07:32.909
side and ten thousand at my right hand, but it

00:07:32.919 --> 00:07:34.749
will not come

00:07:34.749 --> 00:07:34.759
nigh

00:07:38.230 --> 00:07:38.240
me."It

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:39.510
takes

00:07:39.520 --> 00:07:42.550
speaking to the problem

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:43.469
and

00:07:43.479 --> 00:07:45.790
circumstances,

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:07.469
submitting yourself unto

00:08:07.479 --> 00:08:09.430
God, and resisting the devil. It's not God making the devil

00:08:09.430 --> 00:08:09.440
flee; it's you submitting yourself unto God and resisting

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:12.869
him with

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:13.710
the

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:17.430
Word. The devil

00:08:17.430 --> 00:08:17.440
is

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:19.589
not afraid of you, ladies and gentlemen;

00:08:19.599 --> 00:08:21.350
he's afraid

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:23.950
of the Word and the revelation of the Word

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:26.149
because the Word of

00:08:26.159 --> 00:08:29.110
God is sharper than any two-edged sword.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.430
We have that Word

00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:32.440
coming

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:35.110
out of our mouth that quenches all

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:37.870
the fiery darts of the devil. We have

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:40.469
the

00:08:40.479 --> 00:08:42.350
shield of faith, the helmet

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:45.550
of salvation, and that armor

00:08:45.550 --> 00:08:45.560
to

00:08:45.560 --> 00:08:49.389
be

00:08:49.399 --> 00:08:51.150
warriors because of

00:08:51.150 --> 00:08:51.160
what

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:54.070
God's given us:

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.389
the

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:56.630
breastplate of righteousness, the girdle of

00:08:56.640 --> 00:08:58.750
truth, and feet

00:08:58.750 --> 00:08:58.760
shod with

00:08:58.760 --> 00:09:00.590
the gospel of peace. But you have to put it on

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:03.030
and

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:04.509
walk

00:09:04.519 --> 00:09:06.310
it out by faith.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.389
Speak to your mountain. Your mountain

00:09:14.839 --> 00:09:17.350
needs to hear your voice.

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.710
Begging is not

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:30.110
believing. Just like Jesus cursed the

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:32.590
fig tree—even if you don't see it right

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:35.110
away, it dried up 24 hours later.

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.710
You

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:41.110
keep pressing in.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:43.069
Just because

00:09:43.079 --> 00:09:44.430
it didn't happen immediately

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:46.630
doesn't mean it didn't work.

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:48.350
Abraham

00:09:49.839 --> 00:09:51.949
staggered not at the promise

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:53.910
of God through unbelief. He

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:56.069
didn't

00:09:58.150 --> 00:09:58.160
give

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:02.590
up and

00:10:02.590 --> 00:10:02.600
say,

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:04.389
"It must have been

00:10:04.399 --> 00:10:06.110
pizza that night I had the

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:08.150
visitation from the Lord telling me

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:09.590
He made a covenant with

00:10:11.710 --> 00:10:11.720
me."If

00:10:15.470 --> 00:10:15.480
he

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:21.630
had,

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:24.710
he would have lost the blessing

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:28.110
of his son.

00:10:28.120 --> 00:10:30.430
You have to have that

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:35.509
bulldog grit.

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:40.389
"I

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:43.470
will receive my manifestation

00:10:45.079 --> 00:10:48.150
no matter what; I am not moved by

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:50.269
what I see or feel,

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:52.470
I'm moved by what the Word of God

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:09.509
says."If

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:21.829
you want results in your prayer life,

00:11:21.839 --> 00:11:24.710
find scripture to back what you're

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:26.829
praying.

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:16.189
You can't

00:12:16.199 --> 00:12:18.790
get off in la-la land and expect God to

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:21.470
answer prayers that are not biblical. You

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:24.550
have

00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:27.350
to

00:12:30.680 --> 00:12:32.590
have

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:36.629
it

00:12:39.079 --> 00:12:40.750
backed

00:12:42.079 --> 00:12:44.509
by the Word of God.

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:46.790
He says we can

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:49.230
walk in divine health with long life.

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:54.350
He promised me at least 120

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:57.030
years; that's what the Word says.

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:58.470
He

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:00.590
will

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:02.990
satisfy us and show us His salvation.

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:05.750
You have a guaranteed scripture right

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:09.550
there.

00:13:12.750 --> 00:13:12.760
If

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:15.710
someone

00:13:17.959 --> 00:13:20.389
is

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:27.069
dealing with

00:13:27.079 --> 00:13:29.430
depression, instead of saying,

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:32.430
"God, help me,"you speak

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:34.509
to that depression and say, "No, the Word

00:13:34.519 --> 00:13:36.509
of God says He's given me a sound

00:13:38.430 --> 00:13:38.440
mind."Speak

00:13:40.279 --> 00:13:42.710
the

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:44.629
Word over your circumstance

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:47.430
according to 2 Timothy 1:7.

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:50.790
You don't have to have depression,

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:52.069
anxiety,

00:13:52.079 --> 00:13:53.150
or

00:13:53.160 --> 00:13:55.670
fear; you can have good, restful sleep.

00:13:58.759 --> 00:14:01.269
We

00:14:03.199 --> 00:14:05.350
want

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:06.870
you

00:14:06.880 --> 00:14:09.710
to

00:14:09.720 --> 00:14:11.870
be

00:14:11.880 --> 00:14:14.829
encouraged

00:14:14.839 --> 00:14:17.749
and

00:14:17.759 --> 00:14:19.990
walk away with hope

00:14:19.990 --> 00:14:20.000
and

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:22.710
joy.

00:14:29.199 --> 00:14:31.110
The

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:33.310
Holy Spirit lives on the inside of you

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:35.870
and has given us everything we need

00:14:35.880 --> 00:14:38.350
in that beautiful book called the Bible.

00:14:50.360 --> 00:14:52.949
We're on the

00:14:52.959 --> 00:14:55.230
victory side,

00:14:55.230 --> 00:14:55.240
not

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:57.350
the victim

00:14:57.350 --> 00:14:57.360
or

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.590
begging side.

00:15:03.079 --> 00:15:06.389
God

00:15:06.399 --> 00:15:09.389
is

00:15:09.399 --> 00:15:12.230
moved

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.710
by your

00:15:13.720 --> 00:15:16.430
faith,

00:15:16.430 --> 00:15:16.440
not

00:15:16.440 --> 00:15:18.670
just

00:15:18.670 --> 00:15:18.680
